[normal]Why did Defra make an additional payment to NuStar (£413,000) in 2012-13[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The original payment made reflected the outcome of the contractual
[normal] 
[normal]dispute
[normal] between RPA and NuStar, which 
[normal]was formally settled at mediation under the terms of a full and final settlement. 
[normal]A further special payment of 
[normal]£413,000 
[normal]was
[normal] made in 2012-13 related to RPA’s agreed contribution towards the final outstanding site cleanup costs.
[normal]  This was cleared through HM Treasury.
